data.description: Excellent Opportunity! Reasonably priced! Nice, roomy, three bedroom two full bathroom home! Wonderful features! Front patio and covered porch area for those special family gatherings! The home sports immaculately nice wood flooring on the first floor throughout the living and dining area's. This eat in kitchen has plenty of space for your creative visions! The finished basement has it's own full bathroom, and you can park right out back if you need to! Possible extra living space here! Upstairs includes three spacious bedrooms, all with ceiling fans for your comfort. and a tastefully done hall bathroom! This is a must see home.  Buyer Grants may be available, come see this home today!
